## ⚡ Amazon EMR (Elastic MapReduce)

### 📌 What is EMR?

* Managed big data platform
* Used for processing massive datasets

---

### 📌 Supported Frameworks

* Hadoop
* Spark
* Hive

---

### 📌 Common Use Cases

* Big data analytics
* Log processing
* Machine learning pipelines

---

## 📊 Amazon QuickSight

### 📌 What is QuickSight?

* Business Intelligence (BI) service
* Creates dashboards & visual reports

---

### 📌 Key Features

* Interactive visualization
* Serverless scalability
* Integrates with AWS data sources

---

## ⚖️ EMR vs QuickSight

| Service    | Purpose             |
| ---------- | ------------------- |
| EMR        | Big data processing |
| QuickSight | Data visualization  |

---

## 💡 Key Learnings

* EMR handles large-scale processing workloads
* QuickSight transforms data into business insights
* Analytics pipelines often combine multiple AWS services

